а) По формуле косинуса двойного угла: \(\cos 2x=1-2\sin^2 x\)
$$16\sin^4x+8(1-2\sin^2x)-7=0\\ 16\sin^4x-16\sin^2x+1=0$$
Замена \(\sin^2x=t\)
$$\displaystyle 16t^{2} +16t+1=0\Leftrightarrow \left[ \begin{array}{l l}
t=\frac{2+\sqrt{3}}{4}\\
t=\frac{2-\sqrt{3}}{4}
\end{array} \right. \Leftrightarrow \left[ \begin{array}{l l}
\sin^{2} x=\frac{2+\sqrt{3}}{4}\\
\sin^{2} x=\frac{2-\sqrt{3}}{4}
\end{array} \right.$$
По формуле понижения степени: \(\sin^2x=\frac{1-\cos 2x}{2}\)
$$\displaystyle \left[ \begin{array}{l l}
\frac{1-\cos 2x}{2} =\frac{2+\sqrt{3}}{4}\\
\frac{1-\cos 2x}{2} =\frac{2-\sqrt{3}}{4}
\end{array} \right. \Leftrightarrow \left[ \begin{array}{l l}
\cos 2x=-\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}\\
\cos 2x=\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}
\end{array} \right. \Leftrightarrow \left[ \begin{array}{l l}
2x=\pm \frac{5\pi }{6} +2\pi k\\
2x=\pm \frac{\pi }{6} +2\pi k
\end{array} \right. ,k\in Z\\ \displaystyle \left[ \begin{array}{l l}
x=\pm \frac{5\pi }{12} +\pi k\\
x=\pm \frac{\pi }{12} +\pi k
\end{array} \right. ,k\in Z$$
Отберем корни на промежутке \([0,5\pi;2\pi]\) с помощью тригонометрической окружности
Нам подходят корни:
$$\frac{\pi}{2}+\frac{\pi}{12}=\frac{7\pi}{12}\\ \pi-\frac{\pi}{12}=\frac{11\pi}{12}\\ \pi+\frac{\pi}{12}=\frac{13\pi}{12}\\ \frac{3\pi}{2}-\frac{\pi}{12}=\frac{17\pi}{12}\\ \frac{3\pi}{2}+\frac{\pi}{12}=\frac{19\pi}{12}\\ 2\pi-\frac{\pi}{12}=\frac{23\pi}{12}$$
Ответ: а) {\(\pm\frac{5\pi}{12}+\pi k;\pm\frac{\pi}{12}+\pi k:k\in Z\)}, б) \(\frac{7\pi}{12}; \frac{11\pi}{12};\frac{13\pi}{12};\frac{17\pi}{12};\frac{19\pi}{12};\frac{23\pi}{12}\).
